DiredMode enhancements for EmacsForWindows.

* Set `shell-file-name' to ##bash.exe## or ##sh.exe##, not ##cmd.exe##. Otherwise, `find' gets confused. -- AadityaSood

* In Dired, be able to use Windows file associations or open Windows Explorer on a file or folder: <tt>[[w32-browser.el]]</tt> plus DiredPlus.

See also
MsShellExecute,
DiredTweaks.

